+PROG RESULTS urs:1
HEAD Export Node Displacements
PAGE UNII 0

$ Export node displacements for all load cases
LC ALL
NODE TYPE UX,UY,UZ,RX,RY,RZ REPR DLST
END

+PROG RESULTS urs:2
HEAD Export Quad Forces
PAGE UNII 0

$ Export quad forces for all load cases
LC ALL
QUAD TYPE MX,MY,MXY,VX,VY,NX,NY,NXY REPR DLST
END
